Title: The Realest Journey
DateModified: '2019-03-05'
DatePublished: '2019-03-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-realest-journey
SetInCountry: Australia
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Chelsea Pedersen-Brown
AuthorCountry: Australia
Text: "It\u2019s about a young girl who travels through Asia and Europe in search\
  \ of her biological father who left the country before she was born. As she moves\
  \ through each city, she finds answers to a lot of her questions in some unexpected\
  \ ways. This is a emotional tale of adventure and discovery, of both the world and\
  \ herself."
